            <span class="readable">&ldquo;She calmly raised the stun gun to her lips as if blowing away imaginary smoke. With a wry smile, she acknowledged the group of women gathered in her living room to witness her in-home presentation. “And that, ladies, is how you keep from becoming a statistic.&rdquo;</span>
